$ CSS: border properties

{ Applying the border property to a HTML TR element #apply-border-to-tr

  In order to apply the border property to a → development/web/HTML/tags/tr[<tr>] element,
  the table's `border-collapse` property must be set to `collapse`.

  See → https://github.com/ReneNyffenegger/about-css/blob/master/properties/border/tr.html

}

